net\/I5OzGMXJ80dp9V7kJfH6_Q==\/2162009296214738345.png\"\/>、<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/img-ph-mirror.nosdn.127.net\/vV_SvzSL5P7FsVUtgkXshg==\/2170172070539414110.png\"\/>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  C、数据信号D在CP信号有效跳变沿（此处为上升沿）到来之前必须稳定的最短时间称为建立时间tSU。即在CP上升沿到达之前，输入信号D应保持某一逻辑电平不变，以保证输入信号能够被有效的识别出来。数据信号D在CP信号有效跳变沿（此处为上升沿）到来之后必须保持稳定的最短时间称为保持时间tH。"},{"caption":"用或非门构成的基本SR锁存器，其特性方程中，约束条件为SR=0。这说明两个输入信号。","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">不能同时为<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'TimesNewRoman',serif;\">1<\/span>","analysis":""},{"caption":"触发器的输出逻辑电平从1到0或从0到1的转换称为","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">翻转<\/span>","analysis":""},{"caption":"假定锁存器的初始状态为0。对于下图所示的电路和输入波形，输出端Q的波形图为。","answer":"<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/26D5E80CD0BBBE5B3328AFDA588279E6.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  A、由或非门组成的基本SR锁存器的特性是：S = R =0，电路状态保持不变；S = 0、R = 1时，将使锁存器置0；S = 1、R = 0时，将使锁存器置1；S = R =1，无论Q和 原来是什么状态，将强制使两个输出端同时为0。若S和R同时回到0，无法确定锁存器的输出状态；但S和R不是同时回到0时，其输出状态则是确定的。"},{"caption":"在下图中，假设触发器的初态均为0，则Q的波形图为。","answer":"<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/3620FEABBCE46DDF4D39A6F498834B00.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  B、D触发器对应每个CP上升沿，输出Q与其对应时刻的输入D相同。根据这一特点，就能画出波形图。"},{"caption":"在下图中，假设触发器的初态为0，则Q的波形图为。","answer":"<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/88262E8EFDFD95036CDC3A3911F89940.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  A、根据逻辑图，将J、K输入方程代入JK触发器的特性方程，就能得到状态方程Q（n+1）=Q非；又因为触发器是上升沿触发的，所以每来一个上升沿，触发器就改变一次状态。"},{"caption":"用CMOS电路74HCT02或非门构成消除机械开关抖动影响的电路及开关S由位置A到B时波形如图所示，试确定Q端的波形为。","answer":"<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/1D22506C6940446C6C4A300B9501ABA3.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  B、开关接通A点时，Q=0，Q非 =1。当开关触点拨离A点瞬间，由于 Q非 =1的作用，其抖动不会影响Q=0的状态。在开关悬空期间，锁存器保持状态不变。开关触点第一次接通B点，就使翻转为0，Q翻转为1。此时开关触点已离开A点，在Q=1的作用下，即使触点的抖动会使B点电平发生跳动，也不会改变 Q非 =0的状态。"},{"caption":"在下图中，假设所有触发器的初态均为0，则在时钟脉冲CP的作用下，Q1、Q0的波形图为。","answer":"<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/79041A69BBC993C6EF7E20D2F8136DE2.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  C、D触发器接成了翻转触发器，对应每个CP上升沿，触发器Q0的状态都会发生翻转。触发器FF1的时钟CP连接到 （Q0非），即对应着Q0从1跳变到0时，Q1的状态就会发生翻转。"},{"caption":"下图是D锁存器定时图，下列说法正确的是。","answer":"<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/img-ph-mirror.nosdn.127.net\/vV_SvzSL5P7FsVUtgkXshg==\/2170172070539414110.png\"\/><spanstyle=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'TimesNewRoman','serif';color:#0000CC;\"><\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">表示输入数据信号<\/span><em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'TimesNewRoman','serif';\">D<\/span><\/em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">的保持时间。<\/span>,<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/img-ph-mirror.nosdn.127.net\/wpnKKHG_vYYXdUHat7XgaQ==\/896216325947384491.png\"\/><spanstyle=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'TimesNewRoman','serif';color:#0000CC;\"><\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">表示使能信号<\/span><em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">E<\/span><\/em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">脉冲宽度的最小值。<\/span>,<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/img-ph-mirror.nosdn.127.net\/RDBJKECslT1nNSuuCdhAQg==\/6630600473257049228.png\"\/><spanstyle=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'TimesNewRoman','serif';color:#0000CC;\"><\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">表示<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">输出信号对输入信号的响应延迟时间，即输出<\/span><em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">Q<\/span><\/em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">从高电平到低电平对信号<\/span><em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">E<\/span><\/em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">的延迟时间。<\/span>,<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/img-ph-mirror.nosdn.127.net\/tSzi7nZrYIlbmgHzkNC8Fw==\/644014746731884638.png\"\/><spanstyle=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'TimesNewRoman','serif';color:#0000CC;\"><\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">表示<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">输出信号对输入信号的响应延迟时间，即输出<\/span><em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">Q<\/span><\/em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">从低电平到高电平对信号<\/span><em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">D<\/span><\/em><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">的延迟时间<\/span>,","analysis":""},{"caption":"由D触发器构成JK触发器的电路是.","answer":"<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/B76933E04CD427A50DA6AD69AF37BE24.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>,<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/A4A62AEF5311F2CC3BA2F0FD725CC4A2.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>,","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  B、根据上图求出各个触发器的状态方程 ，找到满足JK触发器的特性方程 电路。"},{"caption":"在下图所示电路中，能完成T触发器逻辑功能的电路有.","answer":"<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/2094E9BACFBAE4F380232249527386C9.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>,<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/77B726D3F45226F569396053CE2ACDC7.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>,<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/50F77600E0A037EF6C050F301371C4C7.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>,","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  C、根据各个触发器的特性方程，将输入代入特性方程进行化简看是否能得到T 触发器的特性方程。"},{"caption":"在图示电路中，能完成的逻辑功能的电路有.","answer":"<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/1B8F065B9E21BDA5535ED030EC648222.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>,<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/345087CEC13CCFD4E5B8BF615F5BF4C0.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>,<imgsrc=\"https:\/\/edu-image.nosdn.127.net\/3C1819D61DB183EE97B30D5388EF5DB6.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=890x0&amp;quality=100\"\/>,","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  A、根据各个触发器的特性方程，将输入代入特性方程进行化简."},{"caption":"锁存器和触发器都属于双稳态电路，它们存在两个稳定状态，从而可存储、记忆1位二进制数据。对吗？","answer":"correct","analysis":""},{"caption":"下图两个非门构成的电路就是一个最基本的的双稳态电路。在接通电源后，它可能随机地进入0状态或1状态，且能长期保持这一位二进制数据不变。但因为没有